址: 長和傳考慮分拆環球電訊業務據報香港及倫敦屬潛在上市地點 | 香港01 https://www.hk01.com/article/60271560?utm_source=01articlecopy&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32020237&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=211077665068b2b660bb58d2_04917247"/><published>2025-08-30T15:53:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>e86dafaa1728694fa4b44c269251ebe2</id><title>發達啦！上訴法院裁定全球關稅政策非法</title><updated>2025-08-30T16:01:49+08:00</updated><author><name>我要做富翁</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-30T16:01:49+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573791762"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573791762"&gt;如果關稅最後判無效,股市可以升到嘭嘭聲&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;被判上訴法院裁定全球關稅政策非法 特朗普稱關稅仍有效&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20250830%2Fbkn-20250830060047035-0830_00992_001.html&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=cc52a47343f5f8b82db483cc0b4e9ed2&amp;amp;fid=57" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intn ... 0830_00992_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32020241&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=211077665068b2b660bb58d2_04917247"/><published>2025-08-30T16:01:49+08:00</published></entry></feed>